data.description: Beautiful, updated ranch home, move in condition, meticulously maintained, nothing to do! Three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, bright eat in kitchen, living room with masonry fireplace, and a finished basement with a pellet stove. Nice brick patio for entertaining, entire backyard has newer fence, one car attached garage, storage shed, new roof 2023, heating is oil, central air conditioning, public water and public sewer. Excellent location to shopping and highways! Don't miss this rare opportunity schedule your showing today! ****Seller received multiple offers, highest & best by Tuesday April 16th at 4pm ****
